title: world country label points
name: world country label points
description:
These data are point features depicting countries, as they existed in January 2008.  The points are located near each country's center and provide locations to place markers, graduated symbols or labels.
Note: These points are a mixture of centroids and label points.  Not all points are inside the polygons they represent.
